        "blocks": [
            {
                "type": "rich_text",
                "block_id": "rODvZ",
                "elements": [
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "Hah! It's very funny seeing this a year later, I remember the discussion though didn't really participate. It definitely felt at the time and felt for a few months that we were losing the \"theory building\" part of it...but I've really leaned into the vibe coding side of things and I don't know how to phrase it...maybe new \"theory building\" pathways have opened up for me, and now I'm able to move more comfortably at this new agent speed across a bunch of different products just fine again..."
