        "client_msg_id": "9daf38ba-5e11-457d-85db-f06c384ed462",
        "text": "yeah it always like this. Everyone use Java, Everyone use React, Everyone use Claude Code. The constant winner-takes-all dynamics disempower the individual, which is what I liked about software in the first place, but in practice you jsut have to pay close attention to what everyone else does and try to predict the hype trends. YOU PICKED ANGULAR GO TO JAIL DO NOT PASS GO!",
