        "client_msg_id": "2c7ffd68-5d33-4010-b686-fce2ecfabf85",
        "text": "I would still say its the executing program that is doing the theory prooving, the spec bit is like a proof sketch and not the proof itself. Its just nice we don't have to write the minutiae anymore. I use self-improvement loops a lot at work, so if the running program is used to correct the spec then I guess maybe the spec becomes something closer to being an actual distillation of a theory.",
